{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block body %}
<article>
    <h2>{{article.title}}</h2>
    <div class="metadata">Ecrit le {{article.createdAt | date('d/m/Y')}} à {{article.createdAt | date('H:i')}}Dans la catégorie {{article.category.title}}</div>
    <div class="content">
        <img src="{{article.image}}"  alt="">
        <p>{{article.content | raw }}</p>
        
    </div>
     <hr>
     <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Exercitationem iure aut, nisi magni saepe veniam repellendus? Dolor sapiente accusantium excepturi aliquid exercitationem praesentium eos numquam velit veniam sunt, corrupti perspiciatis nobis culpa at hic quas inventore dignissimos, tempora veritatis harum! Autem voluptatem neque iste sint laboriosam minima quod iure pariatur!</p>
</article>
<section id="commentaire">
{% for comment in article.comments %}
    <div class="comment">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-3">
            {{comment.author}} (<small> {{comment.createdAt | date('d/m/Y à H:i')}} </small>)
            </div>
            <div class="col">
            {{comment.content | raw}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endfor %}
</section>
{% endblock %}